    <item><title>ChristianMahnke.de: New biography of Franz Robert Fritz Neumann (1897-1984) aka Ric available</title>
        <link>https://christianmahnke.de/post/fritz-neumann-biography</link>
        <pubDate>Fri, 18 Apr 2025 07:03:44 +0200</pubDate>
        <guid>https://projektemacher.org/en/post/christianmahnke/post/fritz-neumann-biography/</guid>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;After the identity of &lt;a href=&#34;https://christianmahnke.de/post/ric-unknownartist/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Fritz Neumann and thus Ric could be clarified in October&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.meibohmfinearts.com/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Mark Strong from Meibohm Fine Arts&lt;/a&gt; compiled, condensed and published on &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.askart.com/artist/Fritz_Neumann/11057559/Fritz_Neumann.aspx&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;AskArt&lt;/a&gt; on the basis of the findings from &lt;a href=&#34;https://ric-unknownartist.projektemacher.org/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;my blog&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Without a paid membership, the full biography can be viewed every Friday, otherwise it is also available for free at &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.meibohmfinearts.com/artists/details/2873&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Meibohm Fine Arts&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
